dataLineage.statement:
Note: this layer has Facility IDs and is used within Public Works Cityworks software. Do not alter the IDs. Do not delete features from this layer, indicate they are no longer used.
1) In May of 2011 DeShawn Robins and a Public Works Dept. Parking Division staff member used a hand held GPS and pdf maps to locate street parking meter posts and parking meters as part of a mapping initiative.
2) Data is updated by GPS and notes when a set of parking meters are removed by changing removed data to "historic", or performing minor adjustments.
